{
  "stem": "21310.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we would-- and he wrote poetry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were-- so we would meet there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he would read poetry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we just did all these things just to hold on to our humanity, you know, not to be devoured by, by what was going on around us, although we did lose one-- one friend of mine go typhus and, and died.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, so there were these two parts of life in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was this horrid, constant fear and hunger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the other hand, there was this attempt at culture, life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- Well, let's, let's talk a little bit more about food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I, I, I don't know how my mother got food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But mostly what we had was the so-called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was one part-- you know, a heavy soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she would get somewhere potatoes and some carrots, and, and whatever, some vegetables, and make that soup and bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we were always hungry, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But as I mentioned before, my parents had these, these few gold pieces.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so for money, you, you could get some food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There wasn't-- you couldn't get any steak or filet mignon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you could-- once in a while, you got-- on the ratio cards, you got, I don't know, one egg a week or something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the eggs were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So if you had some money, you could get-- buy some more eggs, for instance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- but mostly, I think it was bread and jam that we were getting on, on ration cards.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- then the, the-- it start-- then in 1942, the great deportations started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And about eight to 10 people-- 8,000 to 10,000 people a day were, were deported.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
